### Hotel Hub API - Hotel Details Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### Note: Replace hotel IDs with actual IDs from your database after ingestion

### Get specific hotel by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}

###

### Get hotel photos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/photos

###

### Get hotel facilities
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/facilities

###

### Get hotel reviews (first page)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/reviews

###

### Get hotel reviews with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/reviews?page=0&size=5

###

### Get hotel reviews (second page)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/reviews?page=1&size=10

###

### Get hotel translations (all languages)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/translations

###

### Get hotel translations (French only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/translations?lang=fr

###

### Get hotel translations (Spanish only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/translations?lang=es

###

### Get hotel rooms
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms

### Test with another hotel ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/{hotelId}

